Subject: [PATCH 05/12] docs: add Effect migration patterns to AGENTS.md
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Document Instance-scoped services, Instance.bind for ALS context
in native callbacks, and the Flag â†’ Effect.Config migration pattern.
---
